active_struct.name: The Dynamic Rollercoaster
attrs: includes both an intro and a bridge, adding dimension and interest to the song
has a repeated chorus that highlights the main theme and hook of the song
allows for storytelling through the verses and bridge

struct_suggs.name: The Melodic Build
attrs: simple and easily recognizable structure
allows for flexibility in song length and arrangement
ideal for catchy, popular songs

struct_suggs.name: The Climactic Journey
attrs: has a strong and dynamic build-up leading to the bridge
includes an instrumental section, adding depth and variety to the song
has a climactic ending in the outro

struct_suggs.name: The Dynamic Rollercoaster
attrs: includes both an intro and a bridge, adding dimension and interest to the song
has a repeated chorus that highlights the main theme and hook of the song
allows for storytelling through the verses and bridge

struct_suggs.name: The Progressive Groove
attrs: has a unique structure that deviates from the traditional verse-chorus-verse-chorus pattern
allows for a gradual build-up and climax through the use of multiple verses
includes a bridge and a final chorus as a strong finale

struct_suggs.name: The Epic Odyssey
attrs: has a defined structure with a clear progression from intro to outro
includes both a pre-chorus and a bridge, providing variety and interest to the song
has a final outro that mirrors the energy of the chorus, creating a satisfying ending

struct_suggs.name: The Interwoven Story
attrs: has a traditional verse-chorus structure with the addition of a bridge and instrumental section
allows for multiple variations and repetitions of the chorus, making it suitable for longer songs
has a strong climax in the outro with the inclusion of both the chorus and instrumental sections

struct_suggs.name: The Exploratory Sound
attrs: includes both an instrumental solo and a bridge, showcasing musical skill and variety
has a strong intro and outro, creating a well-rounded structure
allows for storytelling and development through the use of verses, pre-choruses, and choruses

struct_suggs.name: The Dynamic Collaboration
attrs: has a unique structure that deviates from the traditional verse-chorus-bridge pattern
includes a breakdown or special section between the bridge and final chorus, adding interest and variety
has a climactic ending in the outro with the repetition of the final chorus

struct_suggs.name: The Intense Ride
attrs: has a slightly different structure with the pre-chorus following the first verse instead of before the chorus
allows for flexibility in arrangement, as the bridge can be placed after the second chorus or near the end of the song
has a memorable and catchy chorus that is reinforced through repetition

struct_suggs.name: The Dynamic Fusion
attrs: has a unique structure with the bridge following the first verse instead of the second
includes both an instrumental section and a breakdown/special section, providing variety and depth to the song
has a dramatic and climactic ending with the repetition of the final chorus and inclusion of a special section.
